    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound BMW E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This chassis remains rigid thanks to proactive subframe reinforcement and a refreshed suspension featuring Bilstein dampers. Power is delivered through a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a factory limited-slip differential. The VANOS system has been recently calibrated, ensuring precise valve timing across the power band. While the finish shows light patina consistent with a well-loved driver\u2019s car, the drivetrain and cooling system are in peak operational order, providing a visceral, analog driving experience.",
