    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and reliability, perfect for someone looking for a dependable daily driver that still turns heads. The exterior retains its deep luster, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper consistent with careful city driving. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free environment with premium upholstery that remains supple, showing only light bolster wear on the driver\u2019s seat. Every electronic feature, from the responsive infotainment screen to the dual-zone climate control, functions exactly as it should. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with no leaks or unusual noises; I have followed a strict maintenance schedule, including a recent brake service and a fresh oil change. The tires have plenty of tread remaining, and the car tracks straight and true at highway speeds. I have the service records available to provide full peace of mind. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that has been well-cared for and is ready for the road.",
