    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable new-to-you ride? I\u2019m parting with my car and it has been such a dependable companion! It\u2019s in really solid shape, drives smoothly, and has been well-loved over the years. It's perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to love it as much as I have! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come by for a test drive!",
