      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six power plant and a precise 6-speed manual transmission. This example boasts a reinforced rear subframe and a recently serviced VANOS system, ensuring the mechanical longevity of its high-revving valvetrain. The chassis maintains its factory-spec rigidity with a functional limited-slip differential providing exceptional corner-exit traction. While it displays the honest patina of a car that has been enjoyed, the engine pulls hard to its 8,000 RPM redline with impeccable throttle response. A mechanically sound specimen ready for the canyon or the track.",
